      This context displays actions to manage container/component relations : Exclude - to exclude component from the container List components - to list all components of the container Facets - display the facets context for the container.
      class  JPropertyPanel
      This context displays actions to manage property names: Add property - to add a property name Delete - to delete the property name.
      class  JValuePanel
      This context displays actions to manage property values: Add value - to add a property value Delete - to delete the property value.
